◆ rockx_image_transform_mode

enum rockx_image_transform_mode

Image Rotate Mode.

Enumerator
ROCKX_IMAGE_TRANSFORM_NONE 

Do not transform.

ROCKX_IMAGE_TRANSFORM_FLIP_H 

Flip image horizontally.

ROCKX_IMAGE_TRANSFORM_FLIP_V 

Flip image vertically.

ROCKX_IMAGE_TRANSFORM_ROTATE_90 

Rotate image 90 degree.

ROCKX_IMAGE_TRANSFORM_ROTATE_180 

Rotate image 180 degree.

ROCKX_IMAGE_TRANSFORM_ROTATE_270 

Rotate image 270 defree.
